CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 17, 1955, pg. A28, reads: "Prepare For Big Things - Betty Dunson and her creative dancers are shown in rehearsal at Irene Kaufmann Settlement. Recently they were featured with James Moody and the El Dorados at the Diamond Roller Rink on Nov. 25.  They will perform at Horizon Ballroom at the Gateway Center and at the Greater Pittsburgh Airport on Christmas Eve. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Betty Dunson wearing wrap skirt with ruffled border and two toned bikini top, posing in dance studio, in Irene Kaufmann Settlement
